{"tid":754530,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴美國觀看曼聯訓練：我還沒看到像我這種水平的","createTime":"2018-07-24T12:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T05:42:03.000Z","uid":38189,"like":23,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"30434f5105a137ea0f555495e2f776143168f022","tid":754530,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"虎撲7月24日訊&nbsp;如果曼聯球迷今早醒來時看到了Instagram上關於曼聯的故事，那麼他一定會發現一個驚喜。 &ldquo;大家好，猜猜誰回來了？&rdquo;伊佈在洛杉磯迎接曼聯的到來。這不是關於瑞典人回到老特拉福德的問題。只有曼聯在加利福尼亞進行季前賽，銀河前鋒​​才有機會觀看曼聯晚上的訓練。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯讓伊布去去到他們的社交網絡上向球迷們傳遞一個信息，而伊布用他特有的語氣對他們說:&ldquo;看著曼聯訓練，我看到了很多高質量的東西，但還沒有看到像我這種水平的。看到孩子們訓練得很好很快樂，我的感覺也很好。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n伊布對即將開始新賽季征程的曼聯球迷們說：&ldquo;大家要為這個賽季做好準備，因為有一些特別的事情將要發生，教練也有一些事情要做，所以都要為這個賽季做好準備，大家好好享受吧。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"5723d944ef07149c0f9fd9f7fb79d197179a3bb1","tid":754530,"uid":3454,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:11:03.000Z","msg":"伊布<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/211102_f4acfc9bf38a09f956675e3aa7b5a976.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F211102_f4acfc9bf38a09f956675e3aa7b5a976.png&h=6c280ba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c037fe5863166aae5d2433fb146adfe3a3f6e6","tid":754530,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/211130_9999e157b9c2a9b979680c38402dafe7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F211130_9999e157b9c2a9b979680c38402dafe7.png&h=235735eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfc2f581b932a68108a2a8f42d6d79682e8f3245","tid":754530,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5723d944ef07149c0f9fd9f7fb79d197179a3bb1","tid":754530,"uid":3454,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:11:03.000Z","msg":"伊布<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa